flowchart TD
    Start([Start: Harness First Pass Improvement]) --> Step1[Step 1: Read coordinator.md]

    %% FC-001: Locate Phase Output Rules section in coordinator documentation
    Step1 --> S1A["Locate 'Phase Output Rules' section"]
    S1A --> S1B["Extract rule definitions and constraints"]
    S1B --> S1C["Insert rules into baseline documentation"]
    S1C --> S1D["Verify line count &lt; 200"]

    %% FC-002: Validate Phase Output Rules integration completeness
    S1D --> Decision1{Phase Output Rules<br/>properly integrated?}
    Decision1 -->|No| S1E["Review and revise rules"]
    S1E --> S1D
    Decision1 -->|Yes| Step2[Step 2: Read worker.md]

    %% FC-003: Extract Edit Completeness rules from worker documentation
    Step2 --> S2A["Locate 'Edit Completeness Rule' section"]
    S2A --> S2B["Extract edit-auth.txt registration requirements"]
    S2B --> S2C["Insert completion checklist into baseline"]
    S2C --> S2D["Verify line count &lt; 200"]

    %% FC-004: Ensure Edit Completeness validation chain is properly configured
    S2D --> Decision2{Edit Completeness<br/>properly integrated?}
    Decision2 -->|No| S2E["Review and revise rules"]
    S2E --> S2D
    Decision2 -->|Yes| Step3[Step 3: Read defs-stage4.ts]

    %% FC-005: Validate baseline/RTM instruction insertion in code review template
    Step3 --> S3A["Locate 'implementation/code_review' template"]
    S3A --> S3B["Extract baseline/RTM procedures"]
    S3B --> S3C["Insert RTM traceability instructions"]
    S3C --> S3D["Verify TypeScript syntax &amp; line count &lt; 200"]
    S3D --> S3E["Confirm @spec annotations present"]

    Step4[Step 4: Run Test Suite] --> S4A["Execute 843 test cases"]
    S4A --> S4B["Monitor test execution"]
    S4B --> Decision3{All tests<br/>PASS?}

    Decision3 -->|FAIL| S4C["Identify failing tests"]
    S4C --> S4D["Review error logs"]
    S4D --> S4E["Rollback problematic changes"]
    S4E --> Step1

    Decision3 -->|PASS| Step5[Step 5: Git Push to Remote]
    Step5 --> S5A["Commit submodule changes"]
    S5A --> S5B["Push submodule to origin/main"]
    S5B --> S5C["Commit parent repository"]
    S5C --> S5D["Push parent to origin/main"]
    S5D --> End([Complete: Workflow Improved])

